Package sait.bms.problemdomain

Class Paperback

  • java.lang.Object
    • sait.bms.problemdomain.Book
      • sait.bms.problemdomain.Paperback
  • public class Paperback
extends Book
    Paperbacks have an ISBN, call number, available, total, title, author(s), year of release, and genre. The last digit of the ISBN for a paperback is between 4 and 7. This object is sub class.
    Version:
    Feburary 14, 2020
    Author:
    Jonghyun Park
